 https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Taylor-Swift-live@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Taylor-Swift-live@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Taylor-Swift-live@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>分享了一段<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-new-album-the-tortured-poets-department-3582273">《The Tortured Poets Department》</a>的新视频，并透露了专辑中的一首歌词。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/taylor-swift-live-in-new-jersey-setlist-photos-3448996">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 新泽西演唱会：每个时代的精彩庆典</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位流行偶像将于本周晚些时候（4 月 19 日星期五）发行她的第 11 张录音室唱片，这是 2022 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美</a>获奖作品<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-midnights-review-3332805">《Midnights》</a>的后续作品。</p><p>现在，在专辑发行前夕，这位歌手在 Instagram 上发布了一段动画短片，充满了关于发行的复活节彩蛋。</p><p>视频于昨晚（4 月 16 日）分享，从指向两点钟的时钟开始。这标志着斯威夫特分享的最新线索，其中包含对那个时代的致敬。此前，该时间出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-taylor-swifts-self-directed-video-for-karma-featuring-ice-spice-3448830">“Karma (Remix)”音乐视频</a>中，在她分享的一张咖啡艺术图片中，与洛杉矶 Spotify 展览上出现的时钟相同。</p><p>从那里，摄像机离开动画房间，在地板上显示皱巴巴的纸，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-taylor-swifts-new-music-video-for-lavender-haze-3387935">“薰衣草薄雾”</a>的乙烯基变体，然后进入白色走廊，面对一扇写着“受折磨的诗人”名字的门部门&#39;。然后它会跳出钥匙孔，放大显示 4 月 19 日打开的日历，上面写着“折磨诗人部门发行日”。</p><p>视频的其他细节包括日历上写着“东部时间晚上 8 点音乐视频发布！！”，总计为 14，也是对 4 月 20 日的致敬，这一天也恰好是<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/record-store-day">唱片店日</a>。</p><p>更多隐藏的细节包括斯威夫特在<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/taylor-swifts-eras-tour-kick-off-top-five-moments-from-the-stars-transcendent-performance-3416005">“Eras Tour”</a>钢琴上的照片，大约在她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-tortured-poets-department-final-variant-3595989">宣布带有 3 首额外歌曲的 2 个变体的</a>同时，以及她与密友兼合作者<a href="/artists/jack-antonoff">杰克·安东诺夫</a>的照片，她最初于 2022 年 10 月在网上发布了这些照片。</p><p>看看下面的剪辑。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C513vGiuWoo/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564