塞思·麦克法兰认为没有“充分的理由”结束《恶搞之家》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/seth-macfarlane-doesnt-see-a-good-reason-to-end-family-guy-3618990?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=seth-macfarlane-doesnt-找到结束家庭成员的好理由Alex RigottiWed, 17 Apr 2024 14:42:18 +0000 Music NewsNewsFamily Guy https://www.nme.com/?p=3618990 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Seth-MacFarlane-main-new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="塞思·麦克法兰" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Seth-MacFarlane-main-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Seth-MacFarlane-main-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Seth-MacFarlane-main-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Seth-MacFarlane-main-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Seth-MacFarlane-main-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Seth-MacFarlane-main-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该剧最近庆祝了开播 25 周年</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/seth-macfarlane-doesnt-see-a-good-reason-to-end-family-guy-3618990">赛斯·麦克法兰认为没有“充分的理由”结束《恶搞之家》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Seth-MacFarlane-main-new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="塞思·麦克法兰" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Seth-MacFarlane-main-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Seth-MacFarlane-main-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Seth-MacFarlane-main-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Seth-MacFarlane-main-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Seth-MacFarlane-main-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Seth-MacFarlane-main-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>塞思·麦克法兰表示，他认为目前还没有结束<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/family-guy"><em>《恶搞之家》的</em></a>“充分理由”。</p><p>在<em><a href="https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/tv/story/2024-04-16/family-guy-25th-anniversary-oral-history">《洛杉矶时报》</a></em>为纪念这部情景喜剧 25 周年而发布的新简介中，创作者回顾了该剧令人印象深刻的长期运行状态，并表示：“目前，我认为没有理由停止。</p><p> “人们仍然喜欢它。它使人们快乐并资助一些公益事业。你可以向雨林信托基金会捐赠大量额外的现金，而且当晚你仍然可以出去吃晚饭。”</p><p>麦克法兰还补充道：“曾经有一段时间我想，是时候结束这一切了。此时，我们已经达到了逃逸速度。我不知道有什么理由在此时停止，除非人们厌倦了它。除非数据表明人们只是说，“呃，我们不再关心<em>《恶搞之家</em>》了。”但这还没有发生。” </p><figure id="attachment_3444831" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3444831" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3444831" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Seth-MacFarlane-main-new.jpg" alt="塞思·麦克法兰" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Seth-MacFarlane-main-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Seth-MacFarlane-main-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Seth-MacFarlane-main-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Seth-MacFarlane-main-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Seth-MacFarlane-main-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Seth-MacFarlane-main-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3444831" class="wp-caption-text">塞思·麦克法兰。图片来源：Momodu Mansaray/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>塞思·麦克法兰是<em>《恶搞之家》</em>的创作者，为剧中的多个角色配音，主要是彼得·格里芬、布莱恩·格里芬、斯图伊·格里芬和格伦·奎格迈尔。</p><p>自节目开播以来，他就一直为这些角色配音，不过<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/seth-macfarlane-quits-family-guy-american-dad-until-writers-strike-ends-3444825">他曾短暂退出以支持美国演员工会和美国电视交易协会 (SAG-AFTRA) 的罢工</a>，并在罢工结束后重新开始配音。</p><p>麦克法兰随后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/seth-macfarlane-to-reprise-ted-role-for-new-tv-series-3205192">播出了他的喜剧电影<em>《泰德》</em>的电视版</a>，该电影于今年一月首映。他继续扮演同名角色，并担任导演、编剧、执行制片人并共同承担剧集运营职责。</p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/seth-macfarlane-says-he-regrets-keeping-family-guy-on-fox-3010097">麦克法兰表示他对福克斯电视台仍在播出该节目感到不高兴</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/seth-macfarlane-doesnt-see-a-good-reason-to-end-family-guy-3618990">赛斯·麦克法兰认为没有“充分的理由”结束《恶搞之家》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
